response.overview: Bill O'Neal infiltrates the Black Panthers on the orders of FBI Agent Mitchell and J. Edgar Hoover. As Black Panther Chairman Fred Hampton ascends—falling for a fellow revolutionary en route—a battle wages for O’Neal’s soul.
response.tagline: You can kill a revolutionary but you can't kill the revolution.
response.title: Judas and the Black Messiah
